{"tid":1843494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球王美斯平紀錄，全場11射零入球！","createTime":"2020-01-26T08:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T02:59:28.000Z","uid":173952,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffa6d944a38e57db37ffa7f34adaa719fa57258","tid":1843494,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8c9hYvg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8c9hYvg.jpg&h=01099d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯11次射門都沒能破門<br />\n<br />\n  對陣華倫西亞，美斯的腳風不是很順，他射門的次數並不少，但最終還是沒有幫助巴塞打開局面。<br />\n<br />\n  在失去了蘇亞雷斯的情況下，施迪安讓美斯出任偽9號，而缺少了與他配合默契的蘇牙，美斯也陷入了相對孤立的境況。<br />\n<br />\n美斯全場完成11次射門<br />\n<br />\n  今場比賽美斯已經足夠努力，全場他完成了11腳射門，但還是沒有取得入球，這也追平了他在2017年12月的紀錄。而在美斯無法開胡的時候，巴塞鋒線其他球員也未能站出來，最終敗走梅斯塔利亞。"},{"pid":"6031a5cbf8bd1037bd50e80a209d80ec0a556b57","tid":1843494,"uid":173952,"like":124,"dislike":5,"score":119,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:44:31.000Z","msg":"今場比賽美斯已經足夠努力，全場他完成了11腳射門，但還是沒有取得入球<br />\n<br />\n美斯11射=努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nc朗11射=浪射"},{"pid":"031e4591a8daf4b5c37bac6f605bafdc7c690bed","tid":1843494,"uid":238427,"like":13,"dislike":33,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"6031a5cbf8bd1037bd50e80a209d80ec0a556b57","tid":1843494,"uid":173952,"like":124,"dislike":5,"score":119,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:44:31.000Z","msg":"今場比賽美斯已經足夠努力，全場他完成了11腳射門，但還是沒有取得入球<br />\n<br />\n美斯11射=努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nc朗11射=浪射"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"冇人理你"},{"pid":"fd47f9e8a6283896161ecc6643ec7bd5db4f534a","tid":1843494,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"031e4591a8daf4b5c37bac6f605bafdc7c690bed","tid":1843494,"uid":238427,"like":13,"dislike":33,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"6031a5cbf8bd1037bd50e80a209d80ec0a556b57","tid":1843494,"uid":173952,"like":124,"dislike":5,"score":119,"citedBy":3,"re